{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"**Root cause**: Two bugs in `handleAPIStepContent`:","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329837797Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"1. The `prompt` config value (e.g., `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")`) was passed directly to `os.ReadFile` without stripping the `file(\"...\")` DSL wrapper, so the path was always invalid.","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329841634Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"2. The handler checked `step.Config[\"command\"]` instead of `step.Config[\"run\"]`, so script step content was never returned (the DSL stores it under `\"run\"`).","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329851563Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329859438Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"**Fixes applied** (`handler.go`):","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329863014Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"- Added `extractFileRef()` to strip the `file(\"...\")` wrapper and extract the actual path","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329870408Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"- Changed `step.Config[\"command\"]` to `step.Config[\"run\"]`","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329877852Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"- Applied `extractFileRef` to `script` config values too","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329886268Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"- Added fallback for inline prompts (not wrapped in `file(...)`)","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329891769Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329901227Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"**Fixes applied** (`project_detail.html`):","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329910334Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","message":"- Added `'run'` to the config key display filter in the step drawer","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.329914762Z"}
{"type":"log","step_name":"update-docs","timestamp":"2026-03-08T04:28:16.3299243Z"}
